Q1. What is your understanding of Blockchain?

Blockchain is a system of recording information in a way that makes it difficult or impossible to change, hack, or cheat the system. A blockchain is a constantly growing ledger that keeps a permanent record of all the transactions that have taken place in a secure, chronological and immutable way in a decentralised distributed network.
 
 
